- `authRefreshCallback` → `AuthRefreshCallback`
- `configDirectory` → `ConfigDirectory`
- `loadAuthClient` → `LoadClient`
- `getLoggedInHandle` → `GetLoggedInHandle`
- `requireAuth` → `RequireAuth` (from guard.go, merged into auth.go)

